    "Patient": "Identifies and describes the patient — the PHI master under HIPAA.",
    "Appointments & Encounters": "Scheduled visits and the clinical encounters they become, including the visit note.",
    "Diagnoses & Results": "ICD-10 diagnoses and LOINC-coded laboratory results.",
    "Prescriptions": "Medication orders, NDC product codes and DEA-scheduled controlled substances.",
    "Claims & Billing": "Professional claims, CPT coding and the revenue cycle.",
